 * @section dependencies_installation Installation Instructions
 *
 * @subsection dependencies_install_linux_ubuntu Ubuntu/Debian Linux
 *
 * @code{.bash}
 * # Build tools
 * apt-get install build-essential clang clang-tidy clang-format cmake ninja-build make
 *
 * # Core dependencies
 * apt-get install libzstd-dev portaudio19-dev libsodium-dev
 *
 * # Release dependencies
 * apt-get install musl-tools musl-dev libmimalloc-dev
 *
 * # Testing dependencies
 * apt-get install libcriterion-dev
 * @endcode
 *
 * @subsection dependencies_install_linux_arch Arch Linux
 *
 * @code{.bash}
 * # Build tools
 * pacman -S pkg-config clang cmake ninja make
 *
 * # Core dependencies
 * pacman -S v4l-utils zstd portaudio libsodium criterion
 *
 * # Release dependencies
 * pacman -S musl mimalloc
 *
 * # Testing dependencies
 * pacman -S criterion
 * @endcode
 *
 * @subsection dependencies_install_macos macOS (Homebrew)
 *
 * @code{.bash}
 * # Build tools (Xcode Command Line Tools provide clang)
 * brew install cmake ninja make
 *
 * # Core dependencies
 * brew install zstd portaudio libsodium
 *
 * # Release dependencies. NOTE: musl is a Linux-only project and is not supported on macOS.
 * brew install mimalloc
 *
 * # Testing framework
 * brew install criterion
 * @endcode
 *
 * @subsection dependencies_install_windows Windows (Scoop + vcpkg)
 *
 * @code{.powershell}
 * # Install Scoop (one-time setup)
 * Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser
 * irm get.scoop.sh | iex
 *
 * # Install build tools via Scoop
 * scoop install cmake ninja llvm
 *
 * # Install vcpkg (one-time setup)
 * git clone https://github.com/Microsoft/vcpkg.git
 * cd vcpkg
 * .\bootstrap-vcpkg.bat
 *
 * # Core dependencies via vcpkg
 * vcpkg install zstd:x64-windows portaudio:x64-windows libsodium:x64-windows
 *
 * # Release dependencies. NOTE: musl is a Linux-only project and is not supported on Windows.
 * vcpkg install mimalloc:x64-windows
 * @endcode
 *
 * **Note**: Criterion is POSIX-only and is not available on Windows. Use Docker for testing.
 *
