 * @section dependencies_troubleshooting Troubleshooting
 *
 * @subsection dependencies_trouble_portaudio PortAudio Issues
 *
 * **Problem**: PortAudio not found by pkg-config
 *
 * **Solution**:
 * @code{.bash}
 * # Linux: Ensure the correct package is installed by your package manager.
 * # See the installation instructions on this page.
 *
 * # macOS: Ensure Homebrew portaudio is in PKG_CONFIG_PATH
 * export PKG_CONFIG_PATH="/opt/homebrew/lib/pkgconfig:$PKG_CONFIG_PATH"
 *
 * # Windows: Use vcpkg and set CMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE
 * cmake -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=C:/vcpkg/scripts/buildsystems/vcpkg.cmake ..
 * @endcode
 *
 * @subsection dependencies_trouble_criterion Criterion Issues
 *
 * **Problem**: Tests fail to build on Windows
 *
 * **Solution**: Criterion is POSIX-only. Use Docker for Windows testing:
 * @code{.powershell}
 * ./tests/scripts/run-docker-tests.ps1
 * @endcode
 *
 * @subsection dependencies_trouble_bearssl BearSSL Build Issues
 *
 * **Problem**: BearSSL fails to build
 *
 * **Solution**: BearSSL requires a Unix-like build environment:
 * @code{.bash}
 * # Linux/macOS: Ensure make is available
 * which make
 *
 * # Windows: BearSSL builds via CMake custom command (no action needed)
 * # If issues persist, manually build:
 * cd deps/bearssl
 * make
 * @endcode
 *
